<h3 id="群组图片">群组图片</h3>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% grouppicture [number]-[layout] %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endgrouppicture %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>或者</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% gp [number]-[layout] %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endgp %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li><code>[number]</code>: 图片总数</li>
<li><code>[layout]</code>: 布局</li>
</ul>
<p>例子：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% grouppicture 3-3 %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">![](/images/next.svg)</span><br><span class="line">![](/images/next.svg)</span><br><span class="line">![](/images/next.svg)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endgrouppicture %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
